reviewText:
This was a lot more challenging than I thought it would be, not sure what I was expecting. The good doctor basically shows you an exercise interval workout incorporating exercises to strengthen parts of your body so you can be stronger for certain sexual positions.
I'm glad I bought it although I ordered two in error so I am selling one of them.

I will keep the other & keep it in my rotation. I feel this is a worth while purchase & my heart rate stood right up there, she explains every thing so you can understand & I did feel better in the bedroom!
Good Luck everyone!
